title: Bug 122584: Cascading parameter values cannot be displayed properly in HTML viewer
description:
Description: Cascading parameter values cannot be displayed properly in HTML viewer.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the design file in HTML viewer.
2. Click on the 'Change parameter' button in HTML viewer.
OB: When opening the design file in the HTML viewer, the cascading parameter values are not displayed correctly.
EB: The cascading parameter values should be displayed properly in the HTML viewer.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow the steps below:
1. Preview the attached design file in the HTML viewer.
2. Click on the 'Change parameter' button in the HTML viewer.
